Yea further, It was propheſied by Enoch, the ſeventh from Adam, againſt ſuch Apoſtates as are mentioned in Juda's Epiſtle, ſaying, behold the Lord cometh in ten Thouſands of his Saints [
                        〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                     ] [in Sanctis Millibus ſuis.] To execute Judgment upon all, and to convince all that are ungodly among them of all their Ungodly Deeds which they have ungodly committed, and of all their hard Speeches which Ungodly Sinners have ſpoken againſt him, Jude. 14.15.
